---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Study Tracks
description: Sequenced VLSI physical design learning paths built from concise lab guides.
permalink: /tracks/
priority: 0.85
---
<section class="shell page-head">
  <p class="eyebrow">Learning paths</p>
  <h1>Study Tracks</h1>
  <p class="lede">Curated sequences for faster progress depending on your goal: onboarding, synthesis handoff, or maintaining lab notes.</p>
</section>

<section class="shell section track-grid">
  {% for track in tracks %}
  <article class="panel">
    <h2><a href="/tracks/{{ track.slug }}/">{{ track.title }}</a></h2>
    <p>{{ track.description }}</p>
    <p class="meta">{{ track.steps | length }} steps</p>
    <ol class="track-steps">
      {% for step in track.steps.slice(0, 4) %}
      <li>{{ step.title }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
